         b'ockquote&gt;Do search engines do a bad job at capturing the quality '
         b'of information?&lt;/blockquote&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\nI&#039;m not sure'
         b' that&#039;s what she&#039;s saying; search engines are good at find'
