         b'e point of an assignment is not to find the answer but to learn &lt;'
         b'i&gt;how&lt;/i&gt; to find the answer. Most undergraduate assignment'
         b's can probably be answered using Google and Wikipedia, but hopefully'
         b' at some point in their careers the students will come across a ques'
